features: Quantity: Package includes 3 Mini Artificial Potted Plants. Each small Eucalyptus and Rosemary Greenery Plant comes already set in its own paper pulp pot for easy displaying.

Dimensions: The Artificial Potted Herbs measure appr. 9" to 10" tall, from top of the plant to the bottom of the pot and 7.9" to 9" wide, from tip to tip of the leaves. The paper pulp pots measure appr. 3.07" tall and 2.95" wide.

Color: The Mini Artificial Potted Greenery feature two-tone grey green eucalyptus plants and flocked green rosemary set in rustic concrete-color pots. These vibrant potted plants look so real and you might feel the urge to water it!

Material: Dense clusters of plastic eucalyptus leaves and rosemary foliage set in sturdy paper pulp pots with simulated soil that is made of foam. These Faux Small Houseplants require no trimming or watering and will stay fresh-looking all year long.

Artificial Eucalyptus & Rosemary Potted Plants are perfect for displaying on tabletop, office desk, nightstand, shelf, cabinets, windowsill, fireplace mantel, coffee tables, dining table, toilet tank, counter top, bookcase or any other little corner that needs greenery décor. They also make a great gift for housewarming parties, weddings and holidays.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value, great product - I’ve ordered 3 sets
reviews.reviewText: I love these little plants! I have used them as a filler above my kitchen cabinets. I’ve been so impressed with the quality I have ordered 3 sets of these now! They fluff up very easy and look great.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Just as pictured! These are adorable, I ended up placing them inside a galvanized basket and its perfect. I like that they are all slightly different colors and types.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Mini Plants
reviews.reviewText: I am so glad I purchased these adorable mini plants. They are perfect for my kitchen sill or any small space to add a little greenery. I'm impressed by the fullness and the look! The pots are taupe in color. The value is great for three mini plants.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect accents for small area!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased 2 sets as accents for small areas. The only thing needed was spreading the leaves out, making them more realistic. If you're looking for plants but don't have the time or want the bother of watering or nuturing. These are PERFECT.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: When I open the box they were a bit smaller than what I expected. However once I fluffed them up they filled out a bit. They are very nice and sturdy and seem to be made out of good quality. The base vases all have slightly different markings which adds to The eclectic look I was going for. They will serve the purpose. A little overpriced.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Loved the appearance and size of the product. Looks great in my bookcase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Second time buying these.
reviews.reviewText: These are great! They fool a lot of people, thinking they are real.Thank you seller!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was skeptical about buying artificial plants without seeing them, I didn’t want them to look “too fake” but these are awesome! Perfect for a smaller space, I put them on a ladder shelf for some greenery. They vases are cute and neutral color, the leaves look mostly realistic and after is spread out the stems a bit, they look fuller! Def worth the money!
I love this set of three plants for my coffee table, great size

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on October 29, 2021
reviews.reviewText: These look cute on my tiered tray. The packaging was unsuitable for shipping (from China), and one of the pots were broken in pieces. I couldn't be bothered to deal with customer service as it had taken so long to be shipped. I stuck the greenery into another little pot that I had lying around. It looks fine.
Sehen sehr echt aus und auch die Farbe der Pflanzen ist wie auf den Bildern. Also man bekommt wirklich das was man auf den Bildern sieht. Bin super zufriedeb und würde es jeder Zeit wieder kaufen.
